To run simulations:

  1 - Install dependencies: 
    sudo apt-get install python-numpy python-scipy python-matplotlib ipython python-notebook python-pandas python-sympy python-nose
  2 - Init submodules:
    git submodule init
  3 - Set environment variables (and create cscope data base)
    source setenv.sh
  4 - Run your simulation
    python src/<your_file.py>
    

